---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
---

<ContentSection title="About Me" id="intro">
  <Fragment slot="lead">
    I help companies build and scale their products through effective marketing and growth strategies.
  </Fragment>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 border border-default bg-offset p-6">
      <Icon name="mdi:rocket" class="h-12 w-12" />
      <h3 class="text-center font-bold text-xl">Growth Strategy</h3>
      <p class="text-center text-offset">Building scalable growth engines for startups and scale-ups</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 border border-default bg-offset p-6">
      <Icon name="mdi:bullhorn" class="h-12 w-12" />
      <h3 class="text-center font-bold text-xl">Marketing Leadership</h3>
      <p class="text-center text-offset">CMO and marketing leadership experience</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 border border-default bg-offset p-6">
      <Icon name="mdi:handshake" class="h-12 w-12" />
      <h3 class="text-center font-bold text-xl">Brand Building</h3>
      <p class="text-center text-offset">Creating compelling brand stories that resonate</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</ContentSection>
